# shadow-society-services — project context

NestJS API for **Shadow Society** (Qwen Cloud Global AI Hackathon 2026 · Agent Society). Sibling of **shadow-society-platform**.

## Stack

- NestJS, Mongoose, Passport JWT (+ optional Google OAuth), class-validator
- Global prefix: `/api/v1`
- MongoDB via `MONGODB_URI`
- Default port: `3011`

## Product focus

- **`debate`**: simulations, Judge (Mirror / Shadow), agent prompts, optional Qwen/DashScope LLM
- Health: `GET /api/v1/health`

Auth / users / emails / PAT modules may remain from the starter stack; hackathon product surface is the debate API. Prefer extending `src/debate/` for product work.

## Platform client

The web app calls this API at `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` (typically `http://localhost:3011/api/v1`). See **shadow-society-platform**.
